description: Whether you want to chase a trophy for your record books or you want to host your family for a relaxing time on the big blue, we can tailor a trip to remember! Through the turquoise waters, for Yellowtail Snapper and Bonito, all the way to Sailfish and Mahi Mahi, Amberjack, Barracuda, Wahoo, various Tunas, and many other species. The crew will clean and bag your catch at the dock! There's snorkeling equipment on all trips and it's all included in your charter price. For anglers looking to kick it up a notch, the crew can take you to gorgeous coral reefs for specialized fish and snorkel trips. You can even enjoy a day trip excursion to swim with the pigs or turtles! *Lunch is available onboard for an additional cost. Reserve at the time of booking.
